ler","video_id":"5DktImOYTrA"}]},{"id":107144,"name":"EGGLIA: Legend of the Redcap Offline","slug":"egglia-legend-of-the-redcap-offline","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/egglia-legend-of-the-redcap-offline","created_at":1534335309260,"updated_at":1534360839249,"summary":"The offline version of Egglia: Legend of the Redcap released when the original version of the game was taken offline along with the launch of the sequel in Japan. \n \n\"Follow the story of a gentle elf named Chabo, who mysteriously falls from the sky and arrives on the continent of Egglia. Uncover the mystery of Chabo and Egglia as you explore and uncover new areas of the world sealed away within eggs, and develop the world of Egglia through building houses, summoning spirits, warding off monsters and forming alliances with other races.\"","storyline":"\"Long ago, there was a kingdom known as Egglia. \nMany races lived in harmony in that miraculous land. \n \nBut those happy days came to a sudden conclusion. \n \nThe kingdom was assaulted by ogres, enormous in size. \nWith neither reason or objective, \nthey came on with the force of a natural disaster. \nThe people of egglia were powerless to resist. \nWith one exceptionL the battle-loving race of demons, the Redcaps... \n \nThe war grew ever more violent, \nand the destruction reached almost to the capital. \n \nTo save the world the kingdom's wizard, Kuff, \nchose to seal the land into myriad eggs. \n \nLand after land he sealed, \nand each sank into slumber within its hard shell. \nAnd each dreamed of the day \nwhen it might be awakened \n \n \nHow much time has passed since then? \nOn a small island, \nthe only remaining land in the world, \nand elf cradles a precious egg. \n \nOne day, a demon boy falls into her realm. \n \nA girl born to save the world and \na red-hatted boy once born for bloodshed. \n \nTheir meeting pulls aside the curtains of a new legend.\"","collection":5486,"popularity":1.0,"version_parent":48018,"version_title":"Offl